Class ZoomEvent

  • java.lang.Object

    An event that indicates that zoom level for a specific URL has been changed.
    指示特定URL的缩放级别已更改的事件。

      • getZoomLevel

        public double getZoomLevel()
        Returns zoom level of the web page. Zoom level can be negative when zoom is out, positive when zoom is in and 0.0 when zoom level is reset to default value.
        返回网页的缩放级别。变焦关闭时，变焦级别可以为负；变焦进入时，变焦级别可以为正；变焦级别重置为默认值时，变焦级别可以为0.0。
        Returns:
        zoom level of the web page. 网页的缩放级别。
